{"tid":1981520,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎危害肝臟】受感染醫生康復後膚色似譚德塞","createTime":"2020-04-20T17:08:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T17:52:54.000Z","uid":175314,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bd95a727c4ca666d37717c0e905463c8f88dbe9c","tid":1981520,"uid":175314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T17:08:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">【武漢肺炎危害肝臟】<br />\n受感染醫生康復後膚色似&ldquo;譚德塞&rdquo;</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://appimg.modaily.cn/app/displayTemplate1/dist/index.html#/newsDetail/9736080/0?isShare=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappimg.modaily.cn%2Fapp%2FdisplayTemplate1%2Fdist%2Findex.html%23%2FnewsDetail%2F9736080%2F0%3FisShare%3Dtrue&d=1E6MrqGGcFSEGQF%2FdL0KzaCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=064e3c70\" target=\"_blank\">https://appimg.modaily.cn/app/displayTemplate1/dist/index.html#/newsDetail/9736080/0?isShare=true</a><br />\n<br />\n※澳門日報消息※<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AJrsSpj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAJrsSpj.jpg&h=42c03ca6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎疫情肆虐全球，部分染疫者康復後，後遺症陸續浮現。<span style=\"color: red;\">湖北武漢兩名前線醫生染疫後一度病危，雖然經搶救後挽回性命，但全身皮膚發黑，特別臉部為甚，猶如&ldquo;黑人&rdquo;。</span><br />\n<br />\n綜合內地媒體報道，武漢市中心醫院兩名醫生，分別是心臟大血管外科副主任易凡及泌尿外科副主任胡衛鋒，今年1月底確診感染新冠肺炎，病情惡化轉趨嚴重，一度需倚賴&ldquo;人工肺&rdquo;搶救，幸經過兩個多月救治後終脫離危險期。但兩人卻全身膚色發黑泛黃。<br />\n<br />\n湖北省防疫專家組成員宋建新表示，感染新冠病毒後，身體會與病毒展開一場&ldquo;殺敵一萬、自損八千&rdquo;的戰鬥，&ldquo;命雖然救活了，但全身多個器官受到損害。&rdquo;他又表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">有的重症病人不僅皮膚變黑還會出現脫皮等情況。</span><br />\n<br />\n武漢大學人民醫院發燒門診醫生亦指出，當肝臟功能長期異常，會引起代謝異常，容易導致皮膚色素暗沉。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">陰功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好番都變咗譚德塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91595c52ddf9ca075a7da4bf285b51a6133b58c5","tid":1981520,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T17:10:49.000Z","msg":"唔通譚德菜係中国人???"},{"pid":"c0f191faecb9dd4bbe0b022a43cc0c344acd1250","tid":1981520,"uid":175314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91595c52ddf9ca075a7da4bf285b51a6133b58c5","tid":1981520,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T17:10:49.000Z","msg":"唔通譚德菜係中国人???"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T17:12:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c787e5755122ce187303e6589831b03761b48ba","tid":1981520,"uid":326725,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"91595c52ddf9ca075a7da4bf285b51a6133b58c5","tid":1981520,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T17:10:49.000Z","msg":"唔通譚德菜係中国人???"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T17:33:36.000Z","msg":"譚生可能係中武漢肺炎之後膚色變黑咗 俾中共派咗佢去扮非洲人<br />\n所以中共不知幾信任佢 因為佢絕對係黑皮黃心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffa369032e9c8f04653b2bedfc586ad6bb670cb6","tid":1981520,"uid":175314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2c787e5755122ce187303e6589831b03761b48ba","tid":1981520,"uid":326725,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"91595c52ddf9ca075a7da4bf285b51a6133b58c5","tid":1981520,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T17:10:49.000Z","msg":"唔通譚德菜係中国人???"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T17:33:36.000Z","msg":"譚生可能係中武漢肺炎之後膚色變黑咗 俾中共派咗佢去扮非洲人<br />\n所以中共不知幾信任佢 因為佢絕對係黑皮黃心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T17:52:54.000Z","msg":"黑皮匪心先真<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}